  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view showcases a serene seascape bathed in the warm hues of sunset. The sky is ablaze with fiery orange and yellow clouds, creating dramatic rays that stretch across the horizon. Below, calm waters reflect the vibrant colors above. A prominent bridge spans the water, connecting landmasses on either side. In the middle distance, a ship is visible, adding a touch of scale and interest. The landscape is framed by rolling hills and subtle coastal vegetation. The overall composition evokes a sense of tranquility and natural beauty.",
